details.description: Since I was young, I have enjoyed making and tasting coffee with friends and family. It brings everybody closer together, making this cafe with my family, I hope to bring coffee into this plaza and enjoyment for everybody. We also serve Salads, Smoothies, Ice Cream, pastries, and Breakfast. I hope everybody enjoys this place.

reviews_data.review_text: So happy to have a delicious, neighborhood coffee shop!
Great place for a coffee to go or quick bite! Reasonable prices, great convenient location. Thrilled to have a coffee place in town on the way to uptown!
Delicious
Yummy food and coffee.
Nice place and neat. Kind of eroupian style. Cappuccino and tiramisu cake was amazing.
One of the best Tiramisu I had !!! I highly recommend checking it out. You'll be glad you did !

This Cafe is truly something special. The owners were so kind and welcoming, they made me feel right at home from the second I walked in. I ordered a latte, and honestly, it was the best I’ve had in Charlotte. The tiramisu? Even better, so light and flavorful, it blew me away.

If you’re in the area, please visit. You’ll leave full, happy, and with a warm heart. Definitely my new favorite spot!
Super friendly owners and the curry chicken croissant and smoothies were delicious!
Cute little place to grab some dessert ❤️
Bacon, egg, cheese croissant with a strawberry banana smoothie was absolutely amazing.
Great new coffee spot!
